6) Learning / Certification (LND)

Effort
	1.	Micro-badge (hours)
	2.	Associate-level cert (days–weeks)
	3.	Professional-level cert (weeks–months)
	4.	Specialty/deep track (months)
	5.	Multi-cert expert path (sustained)

Outcome
	1.	Attempt/no pass
	2.	Pass, not yet applied
	3.	Pass + applied within 30 days (in a loop)
	4.	Pass + applied with measurable impact
	5.	Pass + org leverage (enablement, templates, revenue impact)

Secondary: exam score, time-to-apply, downstream loop references.
Velocity tweak: small bonus (operationally) for on-time completion + applied use within 30d.

