7) Advisory / Strategy / Executive (ADVISORY)

Effort
	1.	One-off advisory / review
	2.	Light discovery; initial framing
	3.	Strategy sprint; options/risks/plan
	4.	Multi-stakeholder strategy + alignment, decision package
	5.	Market/partner architecture; ecosystem-scale program

Outcome
	1.	No decision/traction
	2.	Decision deck/recs; no uptake
	3.	Decision taken; initial execution starts
	4.	Decision + measurable business impact (rev, cost, risk)
	5.	Strategy opens a durable new lane (tier/market/flywheel shift)

Secondary: decision latency, adoption rate, downstream revenue/cost impacts.
Velocity tweak: longer arc—score Outcome only when it converts (avoid “deck theater”).

