Aggregation & Credit

Per-person velocity is computed from their credit-weighted loop_scores:
	•	Owner score contribution = 1.0 × loop_score (unless contributors are assigned; then owner share ≥0.5)
	•	Contributor contribution = share × loop_score (each 0.25–0.50; up to 3 contributors)

Work Résumé entries auto-create for Owner (and optionally contributors) on close:
	•	Title, Category, Score, Date, Accreditation flag (for LND), Visibility, Public blurb.

